title: Kevin Smith Show [09.04.07] - Dr. Sarfatti - Physics & Conscious
description:
A nice, little radio talkshow, hosted by an ex-cop out of Arizona. 

The show is very akin to Coast to Coast AM. Same sort of topics etc. But I always end up feeling as if I have received more information from Kevin&#039;s 2-hour show, than what I&#039;m getting from Coast&#039;s 4-hour show.

If you like Coast To Coast AM, chances are that you will like this show, as well.

Learn more @ www.kevinsmithshow.com
